summary: The ice sword Frostbite from Infinity Blade iphone game
descriptionHtml: This here is Frostbite the \"Chillrend\" of the Infinity Blade game series. It has the chillrend enchantment which gives it a white frosty edge all around. The sword is craftable under daedric category and is enchantable/temperable and is one-handed. Dont bitch about the textures because guess what... its not made of metal! Its carved out of nevermelting ice.
author: siberok92
